snippet.title: The Night Ripper - Slasher Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Join my patreon to download and play now: http://patreon.com/puppetcombo

THE NIGHT RIPPER (2017) - As the “Night Ripper” terrorizes the city, Rachel must walk home alone after work. But a short trip goes astray when the streets are cordoned off due to another slaying and she's forced down a back alley. Unfortunately for her, the Ripper isn't done for the night.

Music: Nick Bassett
Editing: kelvinader13 (https://www.youtube.com/user/kelvinader13)
Title Card: Markus Bülow (http://markusbuelow.blogspot.com)
